node.text: Yes this is a 5th wheel not a house. 2021 Avalanche Model 390DS. Owned for 6 months just have a house now so I don’t need it anymore. $60k. Flawless other than missing couch and kitchen table.(the stock ones were small so I used my own) Located in Nashville TN. 2K deposit holds it for one week.

node.text: Are you thinking what I’m thinking?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by WHISTLINDIESEL on August 30, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text.

node.text: It’s not a transformation. It’s a literal transformer 💀 The funny thing is the only original parts on the truck are the engine, cab, and interior. Yes the engine is still literally perfectly fine. I’ve never had one single issue with it 😀 I do have a spare in the bed now though so.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by WHISTLINDIESEL on August 30, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: Stopped by my old house and visited my family since I was going through Indiana. It’s crazy to me that all of this started out of that tiny little garage with my first truck and no tools or help. We’d always come in here for breakfast after hunting when I was little and talk about what we saw. Funny seeing the yard in mint condition 💀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by WHISTLINDIESEL on August 30, 2021 tagging @eddiesoc, @creativelightingsource, @sixtwelveautoworx, and @lgndsupply.

node.text: Always whole ass everything. The permanent set of MM2 mirrors is finally done 😭😍 It’s going to be such a shame when they get hit by a f*cking air strike. @creativelightingsource @sixtwelveautoworx #MM2

node.text: If you want to go tailgating on Monstermax 2 you’re gonna need an oxygen tank, a 24ft extension ladder, and some climbing gear. Honestly how is this even real? 😅 Full video is on YouTube.

node.text: ABSOLUTELY F*CKING ABSURD 😍 MONSTERMAX 2. The worlds largest truck. On TITAN LSW 1400s the worlds largest Ag tires, 8,000lb axles, and an extra duramax in the bed. This doesn’t even look real. YouTube video is live on the new worlds largest truck. Unofficially measured. NEVER LET ANYONE TELL YOU NO. Thanks to @ddpaddy for putting my stupid imagination into reality.

node.text: Come see Monstermax 2 “THE 8th WONDER OF THE WORLD” at the World Farm Progress Show Monday through Wednesday of this week. I’m freaking PUMPEDDDDD.
